high_descs: walk forwards a bit, turn right and go to the kitchen counter
grab the spoon off of the kitchen counter there
turn right and move towards the sink on the left
place the spoon inside an orange cup in the sink
pick up the cup with the spoon in it
turn left and move towards the microwave, then turn right to face it
place the cup on the kitchen counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cup with a spoon in it on the kitchen counter near the microwave

high_descs: Move forward toward the beige coffee maker then turn right and move to the gold dishwasher.
Pick up the spoon on the counter to the right of the red microwave.
Turn to the right and move toward the range, then turn left when in front of the sink.
Place the spoon in the copper-colored wine glass in the sink to the left of the red apple.
Pick up the wine glass containing the spoon from the sink.
Turn to the left and move to the dishwasher and then turn to the right and face the counter.
Place the wine glass containing the spoon on the counter above the middle of the dishwasher and to the left of the pump dispenser.
anns.task_desc: Place a wine glass containing a spoon on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to face the counter space to the right of the microwave.
Pick up the spoon that is on the counter.
Turn right and move to the sink.
Place the spoon inside the wineglass that is in the sink.
Pick up the wineglass with the spoon inside.
Turn left and return to the counter space on the right of the microwave.
Put the wineglass with the spoon inside on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a wineglass with a spoon in it on the counter.
